cz.syntea.xdef.sys

Class SManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.syntea.xdef.sys.SManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SConstants

    public final class SManager
extends java.lang.Object
implements SConstants
    Provides managing of properties, languages and report tables. It exists the singleton instance of SManager. You can get this instance by the static method getInstance(). Note the SManager is used as manager of reports. Therefore in such multi thread applications which requires to have well defined environment for the language, properties and/or message tables you have to synchronize run of such application by: 
    
 synchronize(SManager.getSManager()) {
 ...
 }
